menu_buildjob_channel
[TITLE]The Manual:  Channel Menu[/TITLE]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_BUILDJOB] from the main view and move to a channel.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Channels are selectable buildings until they are linked to a river.  Adjacent channels are joined into one large building.
[B]
The principal use of channels is to connect them to floodgates and move water from rivers to farm or form barriers.
[B]
However, channels can also be filled with water by bucket.  These channels are designated "ponds" and you can place aquatic
creatures that you've captured in them to sooth and entertain your dwarves.
